description: Request to start or continue a multi-part file upload.

contentMD5Hex.description: The MD5 of the entire file to be uploaded represented as a HEX string.

contentType.description: The content type of the file.

fileSizeBytes.description: The size of the entire file in bytes.

storageLocationId.description: The identifier of the storage location where this file should be stored.  A value of null indicates the default synapse storage.
